    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    FCDO privacy notice: coronavirus emergency loans abroad
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office processes your data if you apply for an emergency loan to return to the UK, or if you are waiting to return during coronavirus.</p>

  </div>
</div>

